"Frozen dessert" means:
Ice cream and frozen custard;
Ice milk;
Mellorine;
Sherbet;
Water ice;
Goat milk ice cream and goat milk frozen custard;
Goat milk ice milk;
Quiescently frozen confection;
Quiescently frozen dairy confection; or
Any frozen food product that is similar in appearance, odor, or taste to any of the products listed in this subsection;
Any frozen food product that is prepared or frozen in the same way as any of the products listed in this subsection; or
The mix that is used in any of the products listed in this subsection.
